## Auth (do not bypass)

1. `src/middleware.ts` — intl + session; maintenance; pending; claim redirect
2. `(dashboard)/layout.tsx` — `requireAuth` → approved + `admin_role_id`
3. Each page — `requirePermission(locale, "...")` (DB-backed permission set)

**Panel access:** `profiles.role = staff`, `approval_status = approved`, `admin_role_id` set, not archived.  
**Sign up:** `/signup` → pending (or `/setup/claim-super-admin` if `app_settings.super_admin_claimed` is false).  
**Super admin:** `admin_roles.is_super_admin` — claim once via `claim_super_admin()` or seeded on existing prod.  
**Drivers:** `profiles.role = rider` — **no admin panel access**.

Auth routes: `/login`, `/signup`, `/forgot-password`, `/reset-password`, `/pending-approval`, `/maintenance`, `/setup/claim-super-admin`.

