## Database schema (core tables)

Migrations: `20260518000000_dpd_core_schema.sql`, `20260518120000_app_settings.sql`, `20260519000000_rbac_approval_setup.sql`, `20260520120000_menu_configs_locales.sql`

| Admin / ops | Tables / columns |
|-------------|------------------|
| RBAC | `admin_permissions`, `admin_roles`, `admin_role_permissions` |
| Approval | `profiles.approval_status`, `approved_at`, `approved_by` |
| Ops flags | `app_settings.maintenance_mode`, `super_admin_claimed`, `super_admin_user_id` |
| Menu editor | `menu_configs` (per `admin_roles.slug`, JSON tree) |
| Locales | `locales` (enabled/default/dir; translations in `src/messages/{locale}.json`) |

| Group | Tables |
|-------|--------|
| Workforce | `partners`, `zones`, `drivers`, `driver_documents`, `driver_assets` |
| Fleet | `vehicles` |
| Ops | `deliveries`, `attendance_logs`, `driver_sessions` |
| Compliance | `wrong_actions`, `hygiene_tasks`, `hygiene_submissions` |
| HR | `requests`, `loan_terms` |
| Payroll | `offers` (legacy), `incentive_rules`, `driver_earnings_daily`, `delivery_rules`, `restaurants` |
| Comms | `notifications`, `support_*`, `appointment_slots`, `appointments` |

**RLS:** Staff = `is_admin_panel_user()` on all tables. Driver policies added per mobile module (see handoff doc).

**Enums:** `driver_status`, `delivery_status`, `request_type`, `request_status`, `severity_level`, etc. — see migration file.

