## Storage

### Cloudflare R2 (private bucket — server env `R2_*`)

| Prefix | Path pattern |
|--------|----------------|
| `drivers/intakes/{intake_id}/` | `{doc_type}.{ext}` — admin Add Driver |
| `drivers/{driver_id}/` | `{doc_type}.{ext}` — post OTP link |
| `partners/{partner_id}/` | `logo.{ext}` — `partners.logo_url` stores object key |

Presigned GET for staff UI; see `src/lib/storage/r2-client.ts`.

### Supabase Storage buckets

| Bucket | App path pattern |
|--------|------------------|
| `branding` | `logo.{png\|jpg\|webp\|svg}` (admin panel logo; public read) |
| `delivery-proofs` | `{driver_id}/{delivery_id}.jpg` |
| `fuel-receipts` | `{driver_id}/{request_id}.jpg` |
| `hygiene-photos` | `{driver_id}/{task_id}.jpg` |
| `support-attachments` | `{thread_id}/{message_id}` |

Deprecated (migrated to R2): `driver-intakes`, `partner-logos`, `driver-documents`.

